
The function SMITHFIGURE plots a linear and quadratic discriminant
for the N-P data used by C.A.B. Smith on his review paper on Fisher's 
discriminant analysis and quadratic discriminant analysis. To obtain 
Figure 1 in his paper, just use the following commands:


dataset = 'psychotic'; 
[lda, Sb, Sw, qda]  = smithFigure(dataset);


